<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Reset</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f7fa; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 480px; margin: 32px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #0001; padding: 32px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .logo { height: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .code { font-size: 2.2em; font-weight: bold; color: #d7263d; letter-spacing: 0.2em; background: #fff0f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 0; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center; }
    .cta { display: block; margin: 32px auto 0 auto; background: #d7263d; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center; }
    .footer { font-size: 0.95em; color: #888; text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="../images/rbclogo.png" alt="RBC EduHub" class="logo" />
      <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Hello{{#if name}}, {{name}}{{/if}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for <strong>RBC EduHub</strong>. Use the code below to proceed:</p>
    <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
    <p>This code expires in <strong>{{ttlMinutes}} minutes</strong>.</p>
    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="cta">Reset Password</a>
    <div class="footer">
      If you did not request this, please ignore this email.<br>
      &copy; {{year}} RBC EduHub
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
